edu.iastate.ansci.flip

Class AlleleInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.DefaultSlidable
      • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.AlleleInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Changeable, Slidable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Slidable>

    public class AlleleInfo
extends DefaultSlidable
implements java.io.Serializable
    An object to be used for assigning Epistatic Effects.
    Essentially it just holds a Locus reference and an int representing the Allele number
    See Also:
